name: AVCaptureVideoDataOutputSampleBufferDelegate
desc: Methods for receiving sample buffers from, and monitoring the status of, a video data output.

items.name: func captureOutput(AVCaptureOutput, didOutput: CMSampleBuffer, from: AVCaptureConnection)
items.desc: Notifies the delegate that a new video frame was written.

items.name: func captureOutput(AVCaptureOutput, didDrop: CMSampleBuffer, from: AVCaptureConnection)
items.desc: Notifies the delegate that a video frame was discarded.
